The '''Duros Space Run''' was a [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace route]]. The route connected the [[Corellian Run/Legends|Corellian Run]] with the [[Hydian Way/Legends|Hydian Way]] and passed through major commercial [[Planet/Legends|planets]] in the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]].

